  • public class ManageProfilePage
extends BasePage
    This is the Page Class for Manage profile page in the mobile application.
    User can navigate to this page by going to:

    Profile menu from home page Tab bar
    by clicking on Manage profile menu in the profiles menu list This page class contains MobileElements on this page and functions to simulate interactions with these elements.
